text: The 1921–22 season was Al-Mokhtalat SC's 11th season of football. The club won 1921–22 Egyptian Cup, 1921–22 Sultan Hussein Cup. == 1922 Egypt Cup == == 1922 Sultan Cup == ==References== Category:1921 in association football Category:1922 in association football Category:Zamalek SC seasons
